title: [Caligos Isle, Northeast Vantage]
description: A skeletal tree clings to a nearby ledge, a rotting ship's wheel lodged securely within the grasp of its spindly branches.  Beneath its distorted shadow cast through a radiant moon, a cave mouth gapes like an open wound in the rock face.
